init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Humans are able to create their own mana, and turn it into spells.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But it comes at a price.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Magic users are often abnormal, and some do not survive the experience.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Those who do survive are changed in many ways, some of them not entirely beneficial.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world they wake up to is not the one they knew before.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They see things differently from the rest of society, and they are often unable to function at all during their daily lives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When they encounter the sight of something that can hurt them, or that they don't understand, they immediately have a violent reaction.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In this third volume, the young man known as Andrei is now trying to understand his power.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is a very powerful user of mana, but this causes him to see the world in warped ways that he can no longer relate to.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When he was first introduced, his power was so great that he could summon mana from the air.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He could also cause things to move in unnatural ways.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Unfortunately, he was unable to control it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was unable to make his power do what he wanted it to do.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It also put the lives of all of his friends in great danger.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Even though he himself could not control his power, Andrei came to realize that his friends could.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They could communicate with his power and make it do what they wanted it to.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When people were confronted with his power, they could never resist the urge to manipulate it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They would use his mana to cause things to happen, even though this would often prove fatal for people around them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Andrei's power had become a major threat to the world, and in many ways it was destroying his own life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She is a special child, that from birth demonstrates great power.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She can communicate with Andrei's power and attempt to control it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She can also read people very well, and she is able to figure out what their intentions are.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She can stop his friends from doing what they want to do, but she needs Andrei's help in order to do so.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She is well aware that Andrei himself cannot control his power and that he has no idea what it is capable of.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is really Emmy who is the great hero in this story.
